Class ConfluenceAttachmentReportConfig

    The configuration object for the Confluence Report.

                                        @NotNull
                                        java.lang.String comment)

        The configuration object for the Confluence Report.

        Parameters:
        repositoryName - The name of the repository for which the report should be generated
        filename - The filename the uploaded report should have in confluence
        baseURL - The baseURL of the Confluence Server with the format protocol://host:port
        path - The Context path of the Confluence Server, for /
        username - The username of a confluence user with access to the Executable Documents.
        password - The password of the confluence user given by username.
        comment - A comment that is added to the attachment
